title: Lynyrd Skynyrd - Lots of Skynyrd (26+ albums)
description:
I am new at this so if this is not organized very well I am sorry. What this is would be a lot of Lynyrd Skynyrd music. There Are 30+ plus disks here(not albums, some albums are 2 disks). It might take you some time to arrange it all to your liking.  

Here is a list of the albums

Gold and Platinum

1991

Christmas Time Again
